{"body": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"setcookie\">\n<span id=\"id1\"></span><h1>setCookie</h1>\n<p>Adds a header to the response to request the update of the cookie with the given name on the client.</p>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"signature\">\n<h2>Signature</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight-scala\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span class=\"k\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">setCookie</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">first</span><span class=\"k\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">HttpCookie</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">more</span><span class=\"k\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">HttpCookie*</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"k\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Directive0</span> \n</pre></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"description\">\n<h2>Description</h2>\n<p>Use the <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../deleteCookie/#deletecookie\"><em>deleteCookie</em></a> directive to delete a cookie.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"example\">\n<h2>Example</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight-scala\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span class=\"k\">val</span> <span class=\"n\">route</span> <span class=\"k\">=</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">setCookie</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"nc\">HttpCookie</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;userName&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">content</span> <span class=\"k\">=</span> <span class=\"s\">&quot;paul&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">))</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">complete</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;The user was logged in&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"o\">}</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"nc\">Get</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;/&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">~&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">route</span> <span class=\"o\">~&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">check</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">responseAs</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">String</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">===</span> <span class=\"s\">&quot;The user was logged in&quot;</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">header</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">`Set-Cookie`</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">===</span> <span class=\"nc\">Some</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">`Set-Cookie`</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"nc\">HttpCookie</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;userName&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">content</span> <span class=\"k\">=</span> <span class=\"s\">&quot;paul&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">)))</span>\n<span class=\"o\">}</span>\n</pre></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n", "display_toc": true, "title": "setCookie", "sourcename": "", "customsidebar": null, "current_page_name": "documentation/spray-routing/cookie-directives/setCookie", "next": {"link": "../../debugging-directives/", "title": "DebuggingDirectives"}, "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"], ["documentation/spray-routing/debugging-directives/index", "DebuggingDirectives", "N", "next"], ["documentation/spray-routing/cookie-directives/optionalCookie", "optionalCookie", "P", "previous"]], "meta": {}, "parents": [{"link": "../../../", "title": "Documentation"}, {"link": "../../", "title": "spray-routing"}, {"link": "../../predefined-directives-by-trait/", "title": "Predefined Directives (by trait)"}, {"link": "../", "title": "CookieDirectives"}], "sidebars": null, "toc": "<ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#\">setCookie</a><ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#signature\">Signature</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#description\">Description</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#example\">Example</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n", "prev": {"link": "../optionalCookie/", "title": "optionalCookie"}, "metatags": ""}